ady, Pat|Pat Ready}}\n|RF\n|data-sort-value=\"930630.930630\"|\n*Joined on June 30\n*Played only one game\n|No\n|<ref name=Ready>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=ready-001pat|title=Pat Ready Minor League Statistics & History|work=Baseball-Reference|publisher=Sports Reference|accessdate=March 13, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center\"|{{sort|Smith|Smith}}\n|RF\n|data-sort-value=\"930706.930808\"|\n*Joined on July 6\n*Left team on August 8\n|No\n|<ref name=Smith>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=smith-256---|title=Smith Minor League Statistics & History|work=Baseball-Reference|publisher=Sports Reference|accessdate=March 13, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center\"|{{sort|Sowders|Sowders}}\n|CF\n|data-sort-value=\"930704.930704\"|\n*Joined on July 4\n*Played only one game\n|No\n|<ref name=Sowders>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=sowder004---|title=Sowders Minor League Statistics & History|work=Baseball-Reference|publisher=Sports Reference|accessdate=March 13, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center\"|{{sort|Sullivan|Sullivan}}\n|LF/RF\n|data-sort-value=\"930810.930811\"|\n*Joined on August 10\n*Played remainder of season\n|No\n|<ref name=Sullivan>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=sulliv094---|title=Sullivan Minor League Statistics & History|work=Baseball-Reference|publisher=Sports Reference|accessdate=March 13, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center\"|{{sortname|Ted|Sullivan|dab=baseball}}\n|RF/P\n|data-sort-value=\"930410.930726\"|\n*First played himself on June 20\n*Left team on July 26\n|Yes\n|<ref name=TSullivan/>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center\"|{{sortname|Kid|Summers}}\n|C\n|data-sort-value=\"930410.930726\"|\n*On Opening Day roster\n*Left team on July 26\n|Yes\n|<ref name=Summers>{{cite web|url=https://www.ba