mand Korea]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCNORTH flash.png|<center>[[United States Northern Command|Special Operations Command North]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCPAC flash.png|<center>[[Special Operations Command Pacific]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCSOUTH flash.svg|<center>[[United States Southern Command#Special Operations Command South|Special Operations Command South]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:United States Army Civil Affairs and Psychological Operations Command (USACAPOC) beret flash.png|<center>[[United States Army Civil Affairs and Psychological Operations Command|US Army Civil Affairs and Psychological Operations Command]]</center>\nFile:USASOC flash.gif|<center>[[United States Army Special Operations Command|US Army Special Operations Command]]</center>\nFile:XVIII Airborne Corps BF.svg|<center>[[XVIII Airborne Corps]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Ordnance Corps (United States Army)|Ordnance]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:28 Ord Co beret flash.png|<center>[[52nd Ordnance Group (EOD)|52nd Ordnance Group]], 192nd Ordnance Battalion's 28th Ordnance Company</center>\nFile:722nd Ordnance Co beret flash.png|<center>52nd Ordnance Group, 192nd Ordnance Battalion's 722nd Ordnance Company</center>\nFile:767th Ordnance Co beret flash.png|<center>52nd Ordnance Group, 192nd Ordnance Battalion's 767th Ordnance Company</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Psychological operations (United States)|Psychological Operations]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:US Army 15th PSYOP BN Flash.png|<center>[[2nd Psychological Operations Group|2nd Psychological Operations (PSYOP) Group's]] 15th PSYOP Battalion</center>\nFile:US_Army_4th_Military_Information_Support_Group_Flash.png|<center>[[4th Psychological Operations Group|4th PSYOP Group]]</center>\nFile:US Army 3rd MISB Flash.png|<center>4th PSYOP Group's 3rd PSYOP Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 7th MISB Flash.png|<center>4th PSYOP Group's 7th PSYOP Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 8th MSIB Flash.png|<center>4th PSYOP Group's 8th PSYOP Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 301st Tactical PSYOP Co Flash.png|<center>[[7th Psychological Operations Group|7th PSYOP Group]], 14th PSYOP Battalion's 301st Tactical PSYOP Company</center>\nFile:US Army 344th Tactical PSYOP Co Flash.png|<center>7th PSYOP Group, 17th PSYOP Battalion's 344th Tactical PSYOP Company</center>\nFile:US Army 345th Tactical PSYOP Co Flash.png|<center>7th PSYOP Group, 17th PSYOP Battalion's 345th Tactical PSYOP Company</center>\nFile:US_Army_8th_Military_Information_Support_Group_Flash.png|<center>[[8th Psychological Operations Group|8th PSYOP Group]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Public affairs (military)|Public Affairs]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:Golden knights beret flash.gif|<center>[[United States Army Recruiting Command|Marketing and Engagement Brigade]]'s [[United States Army Parachute Team|US Army Parachute Team]]</center>\nFile:US Army 49th Public Affairs Detachment Flash.png|<center>82nd Airborne Division's 49th Public Affairs Detachment</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Quartermaster Corps (United States Army)|Quartermaster]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:Defense Logistics Agency-Defense Distribution Depot-Army Element Flash.png|<center>[[Defense Logistics Agency]]'s Defense Distribution Depot-Army Element</center>\nFile:US Army 647th Quartermaster Company Flash.png|<center>[[3rd Sustainment Command (Expeditionary)|3rd Expeditionary Sustainment Command]], [[264th Combat Sustainment Support Battalion]]'s 647th Quartermaster Company</center>\nFile:US Army 294th Quartermaster Company Flash.png|<center>[[Sustainment Brigades in the United States Army|36th Sustainment Brigade]]'s 294th Quartermaster Company</center>\nFile:US Army 36th Quartermaster Detachment Beret Flash.png|<center>36th Sustainment Brigade, 294th Quartermaster Company's 36th Quartermaster Detachment</center>\nFile:US Army 861st Quartermaster Company Flash.png|<center>[[77th Sustainment Brigade]]'s 861st Quartermaster Company</center>\nFile:US Army 824th Quartermaster Company Flash.svg|<center>[[82nd Sustainment Brigade]]'s 824th Quartermaster Company</center>\nFile:US Army 346th Quartermaster Company Flash.png|<center>[[518th Sustainment Brigade (United States)|518th Sustainment Brigade's]] 346th Quartermaster Company</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Signal Corps (United States Army)|Signal]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:USSOCOM-JSOC-JCU Beret Flash-Army Element.svg|<center>[[Joint Special Operations Command]]'s [[Joint Communications Unit]]\u2013Army element</center>\nFile:US Army 55st Signal Company Flash.png|<center>[[7th Signal Command (United States)|21st Signal Brigade's]] 55th Signal Company</center>\nFile:US Army 982nd Signal Company Flash.png|<center>[[335th Theater Signal Command (United States)|359th Signal Brigade's]] 982nd Signal Company</center>\nFile:US Army 112th SIG BN Flash.svg|<center>[[528th Sustainment Brigade (United States)|528th Sustainment Brigade's]] [[112th Special Operations Signal Battalion]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Special Forces (United States Army)|Special Forces]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:US Army 1st Special Forces Command-Joint Staff Element flash.svg|<center>Special Forces personnel assigned to the [[Joint Chiefs of Staff]]</center>\nFile:US Army Special Forces Personnel in non-Special Forces units flash.png|<center>Special Forces personnel in non-special operations units</center>\nFile:US Army 1st Special Forces Command Flash.png|<center>[[1st Special Forces Command (Airborne)|1st Special Forces Command]]</center>\nFile:1sfg.png|<center>[[1st Special Forces Group (United States)|1st Special Forces Group]]</center>\nFile:US Army 39th SFD Beret Flash.png|<center>1st Special Forces Group's 39th Special Forces Detachment</center>\nFile:3sfg.svg|<center>[[3rd Special Forces Group (United States)|3rd Special Forces Group]]</center>\nFile:5th SFG Beret Flash.png|<center>[[5th Special Forces Group (United States)|5th Special Forces Group]]</center>\nFile:7th Special Forces Group.svg|<center>[[7th Special Forces Group (United States)