ta/gobierno-decreto-tres-dias-de-duelo-oficial-por-muerte-de-chavez--20133611490 Gobierno decret\u00f3 tres d\u00edas de duelo oficial por muerte de Ch\u00e1vez]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Dominican Republic}}\n| <ref>[https://www.diariolibre.com/actualidad/three-days-of-mourning-for-chavez-dm-will-go-to-venezuela-HMDL374223 Three days of mourning for Chavez; DM will go to Venezuela]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Cuba}}\n| 2\n| <ref name=Chavez/>\n|-\n| {{flag|Iran}}\n| rowspan=2| 1\n| <ref name=Chavez/><ref>[https://www.reuters.com/article/us-venezuela-chavez-iran/iran-declares-day-of-mourning-for-anti-u-s-ally-chavez-idUSBRE9250CQ20130306 Iran declares day of mourning for anti-U.S. ally Chavez]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Dominica}}\n| <ref>[https://dominicanewsonline.com/news/homepage/news/politics/pm-declares-national-state-of-mourning/ PM declares National State of Mourning]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Romania}}\n| rowspan=2| 2013\n| rowspan=2| 1\n| rowspan=2| Victims of the [[2013 Podgorica bus crash]] in [[Montenegro]]\n| All of the victims were Romanian citizens.<ref name=Romania/><ref>[http://www.cdep.ro/pls/legis/legis_pck.htp_act?ida=118385 HOT\u0102R\u00c2RE nr.410 din 25 iunie 2013]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Montenegro}}\n| <ref>[https://www.b92.net/eng/news/region.php?yyyy=2013&mm=06&dd=26&nav_id=86750 Day of mourning in Montenegro for victims of two accidents]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Poland}}\n| 2013\n| 1\n| Death of former Prime Minister [[Tadeusz Mazowiecki]]\n| <ref>[https://www.prezydent.pl/en/president-komorowski/news/art,521,national-mourning-for-tadeusz-mazowiecki-on-november-3.html National mourning for Tadeusz Mazowiecki on November 3]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Algeria}}\n| 2014\n| 3\n| Victims of the [[2014 Algerian Air Force C-130 crash]]\n| <ref>[https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-algeria-crash/algerian-military-plane-crashes-into-mountain-77-killed-idUKBREA1A0YF20140211 Algerian military plane crashes into mountain, 77 killed]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Ukraine}}\n| 2014\n| 1\n| Victims of the 