yn/magazyn/prasowka-sprzed-lat/prasowka-sprzed-lat--wokol-walczacej-warszawy-5-pazdziernika-1944-r.html |website=Nasz Swiat |language=pl |date=October 5, 2014}}</ref><ref name=PolandMourning/>\n|-\n| {{flag|United States}}\n| 1945\n| 1\n| Death of U.S. President [[Franklin D. Roosevelt]]\n| <ref name=USStateFunerals/>\n|-\n| {{flag|India}}\n| 1948\n| 13\n| [[Assassination of Mahatma Gandhi]]\n| <ref>{{cite web |title=Assassination of Mr Gandhi |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/1948/jan/31/india.fromthearchive |website=The Guardian |date=January 13, 1948}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==1950s==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"  style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n! Country\n! Year\n! Days of mourning\n! Reason\n! Notes\n|-\n| {{flag|United Kingdom}}\n| 1952\n| 9\n| Death of King [[George VI]]\n| \n|-\n| {{flag|Argentina}}\n| 1952\n| 30\n| Death of [[First Ladies and Gentlemen of Argentina|First Ladies]] Argentina [[Eva Per\u00f3n]]\n| <ref>{{cite web |title=Argentina Returns Body of Eva Peron To Exiled Husband |url=https://www.nytimes.com/1971/09/04/archives/argentina-returns-body-of-eva-peron-to-exiled-husband-argentina.html |website=The New York Times |date=September 4, 1971}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Netherlands}}\n| 1953\n| 1\n| Victims of the [[North Sea flood of 1953|North Sea flood of 1953 (watersnoodramp)]]\n| <ref>{{cite web |title=Een wit rouwkleed lag over Nederland |url=https://www.delpher.nl/nl/kranten/view?coll=ddd&identifier=ddd:010677206:mpeg21:a0001 |publisher=Nieuwsblad van het Noorden |language=nl |date=February 9, 1953}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Soviet Union}}\n| rowspan=2| 1953\n| 4\n| rowspan=2| [[Death and state funeral of Joseph Stalin|Death]] of Soviet leader [[Joseph Stalin]]\n| <ref>{{cite web |last1=Gessen |first1=Masha |title=A Hypnotic but Contextless Portrait of Stalin\u2019s Death and Its Aftermath |url=https://www.newyorker.com/news/our-columnists/a-hypnotic-but-contextless-portrait-of-stalins-death-and-its-aftermath |website=The New Yorker |date=September 30, 2019