85 HOT\u0102R\u00c2RE nr.410 din 25 iunie 2013]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Montenegro}}\n| <ref>[https://www.b92.net/eng/news/region.php?yyyy=2013&mm=06&dd=26&nav_id=86750 Day of mourning in Montenegro for victims of two accidents]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Poland}}\n| 2013\n| 1\n| Death of former Prime Minister [[Tadeusz Mazowiecki]]\n| <ref>[https://www.prezydent.pl/en/president-komorowski/news/art,521,national-mourning-for-tadeusz-mazowiecki-on-november-3.html National mourning for Tadeusz Mazowiecki on November 3]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Algeria}}\n| 2014\n| 3\n| Victims of the [[2014 Algerian Air Force C-130 crash]]\n| <ref>[https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-algeria-crash/algerian-military-plane-crashes-into-mountain-77-killed-idUKBREA1A0YF20140211 Algerian military plane crashes into mountain, 77 killed]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Ukraine}}\n| 2014\n| 1\n| Victims of the [[2014 Ukrainian Air Force Il-76 shootdown]]\n| <ref>[https://www.euronews.com/2014/06/15/ukraine-declares-national-day-of-mourning Ukraine declares national day of mourning]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Bulgaria}}\n| 2014\n| 1\n| Victims of the [[2014 Bulgarian floods]]\n| <ref>[https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/613037/12-die-in-flooding-in-bulgaria-after-heavy-rain 12 die in flooding in Bulgaria after heavy rain]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Netherlands}}\n| rowspan=3| 2014\n| rowspan=3| 1\n| rowspan=3| Victims of the shootdown of [[Malaysia Airlines Flight 17]] in [[Ukraine]]\n| 193 Dutch citizens were among those killed. First national day of mourning in the Netherlands since the [[assassination of John F. Kennedy]] in 1963.<ref>[https://www.france24.com/en/20140723-netherlands-mh17-victims-mourning-warship-france-russia Netherlands holds day of mourning for victims of flight MH17]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Malaysia}}\n| 43 Malaysian citizens were among those killed.<ref>[https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-malaysia-airplane-mourning/malaysia-declares-aug-22-national-day-of-mourning-for-mh17-victims-idUKKBN0GE0WV20140814 Malaysia declares Aug